{"tid":201313,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［層壓式］好撚不安 求助","createTime":"2017-04-14T16:01:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T01:18:48.000Z","uid":74490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0e505b6ebada956128d46a6f8e1bf458aba24a8e","tid":201313,"uid":74490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T16:01:22.000Z","msg":"借朋友ac開post<br />\n我老母好似中撚左啲層壓式騙局  佢有個朋友叫佢投資 MFCClub  之後我上網search過有關於MFCClub嘅新聞話係詐騙嘅 <br />\n新聞link <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160805/922924/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20160805%2F922924%2F&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=9ba0f585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160805/922924/</a><br />\n<br />\n但性質唔同 新聞講緊好似關於要儲遊戲幣 但我老母個邊好似係純粹投資<br />\n我比左老母睇個新聞佢都唔撚信我 我頭先同老母講依畢錢本身係買教訓 佢仲屌我叫我唔好潑冷水佢個朋友都賺到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我老母仲扔左十幾萬入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我知道會回返本嘅機率唔高 我知道關於依個投資嘅野都好少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為每次老母出去同個朋友疑似做買賣個陣我都唔得閒陪佢去 所以我講嘅野都未必係100%正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我都唔confirm佢間野算唔算係層壓式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同老母講完佢可能比人呃又唔撚信我 好撚不安 我應該點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無人話我知依間野係咪做緊層壓式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？如果係我又要點樣做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"7629ab1e226208d9095b769cb7d2ff71ecc4549c","tid":201313,"uid":354536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"